Hey Alan,

This ticket is just a record of the update we completed today for ticket #00429627 to address an issue with the SQL data collector.

Upgraded from:

	NEA v11.6.0.90
	Sensitive Data Discovery v11.6.0.12


Upgraded to:


	NEA v11.6.0.137
	SDD v11.6.0.18

The patch notes for the latest build can now be found on our Netwrix Community site:
https://community.netwrix.com/t/version-11-6-release-notes-bug-fixes/274/3

I will proceed with closing this ticket out. Ticket #00429627 will remain open until I get word we are successfully scanning SQL.

Thank you,

Tay Caliguiri
